      "content": "The sentiment of the community posts is overwhelmingly negative. They express frustration and opposition to the new zoning and housing laws. The underlying reasoning is that these changes threaten the existing neighborhood community, potentially displacing long-term residents and bringing unwanted changes like increased noise and gentrification. They fear the loss of cultural and societal identity and the potential feeling of powerlessness against these changes.",
